data.description: WELCOME HOME!! GORGEOUS MOVE IN READY 2256 sq. ft. 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath home updated in 2023 with a new kitchen, new bathrooms, new flooring and new roof installed in 2021.  You will be drawn in once you open the door with its high ceilings and large open floor plan.  The kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances throughout, solid white cabinets and a large island with plenty of space to work or enjoy those family gatherings. The split bedroom floor plan allows for the ultimate privacy for family or entertaining guests. The master suite features large walk-in closets and spacious bathroom with a soaking tub with separate shower.  Great schools.  Close to 1-95 and beaches.
